{"id": "1516031770347311124", "channel_id": "1516031770347311124", "type": 0, "author_id": "1470253170209853632", "author_name": "morimensstaff03", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人你好：\n       弥萨格大学校务处将于6月15日18:40(UTC+8) 进行校内设施修复，更新完成后您将得到通知，重新进入游戏。对于更新可能给大家带来的不便，我们会准备一份补给物资以示歉意。祝大家调查顺利！ \n  \n【补给物资】\n在线维护补偿：银芯×50\n  \n【领取条件】\n领取时间截至2026年6月29日23:59。请记得及时前往邮箱领取补给物资哦。  \n \n【更新内容】\n● 修复了活动「无形交响」中「轰鸣之音-迷途梦引」关卡的「重现确认」奖励预览中，「灵知制剂」也会错误地显示「乐章加成」的问题。修复后实际获得不受影响。\n    ○ 对于本次预览显示错误给守密人造成的困扰，我们深表歉意，将为全体守密人发放「特批药剂」×5 的补偿。\n    ○ 如有异议请联系客服进行相应的「灵啡肽」退还，我们将在退还「灵啡肽」时一并扣除重现所得。", "timestamp": "2026-06-15T10:49:00.559000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1516031770502496337", "filename": "screenshot_2026-04-29_17-10-25.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 801524, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1516031770347311124/1516031770502496337/screenshot_2026-04-29_17-10-25.png?ex=6a312a1c&is=6a2fd89c&hm=38f4e01dca1d7f5a83f200e825abea09bccd7a3091a6fbd3bf60967efbcd25a0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1516031770347311124", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1.6 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1516031825980555304", "channel_id": "1516031770347311124", "type": 0, "author_id": "1470253170209853632", "author_name": "morimensstaff03", "author_bot": false, "content": "**V2.5.1.6 Online Maintenance Announcement**\n\n\nDear Keeper,\nThe Mythag Administration Office will conduct campus facility maintenance on  June 15, 2026 at 18:40(UTC+8) . You will be notified once the update is complete and you can re-enter the game. As an apology for any inconvenience caused by the update, we will provide a supply package. Wishing everyone a successful investigation!\n   \n[Compensation]\nOnline Maintenance Compensation: Silver×50\n   \n[Claim Conditions]\nThe claiming time ends on June 29, 2026 at 23:59. Please remember to go to your mailox in time to claim the supply materials.\n   \n[Update Content]\n● Fixed an issue in the \"Invisible Symphony\" event where the \"Reenact Confirmation\" reward preview for the \"Roaring Machines-Lost Dream's Guide\" Stage incorrectly displayed \"Movement Bonus\" for \"Gnosis Elixir\". Actual rewards obtained are not affected after the fix.\n○ We sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused to all Keepers by the display error in this preview, and will be distributing \"Special Potion Supply\" ×5 as compensation to all Keepers.\n○ If you have any objections, please contact customer service for the corresponding \"Menophin\" refund. We will deduct the Reenact earnings at the same time as the \"Menophin\" refund is processed.", "timestamp": "2026-06-15T10:49:13.823000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Tinct_shy", "emoji_id": "1356053151349997829", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Tulu_sleepy", "emoji_id": "1468258202129928387", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1516031770347311124", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1.6 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
